Package farkleapp

This is the package containing the Farkle MVC JavaFX Application.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FarkleControllerInterface
    This specifies our MV Controller Interface layout.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    This is the controller class for Farkle.
    DiceImages
    This class contains the images for our application and our model to use.
    FarkleApp
    FarkleApp is the base class for the Farkle game.
    GameAlerts
    This class is a Model to View Alerts helper class for our model.
    Model
    The Model class interfaces with Controller and FarkleDiceLogic to map the numerical logic done on our dice to a visual representation usable by our JavaFX controller.
